  "text": "On the other hand, Bellamy et al. [CITATION_1] performed a systematic review and meta-analysis to quantify the risk of future cardiovascular disease, cancer, and mortality after preeclampsia finding increased risk for cardiovascular risk, but no association to any cancer was found. Unfortunately, we could not find information about this issue in studies based in LatinAmerican countries.",
